            <li><strong>Lower Energy Bills:</strong> A well-maintained AC operates 15-25% more efficiently than a neglected one, saving money every month.</li>
            <li><strong>Extend Equipment Life:</strong> Regular maintenance can extend your AC's lifespan from 10-12 years to 15-20 years.</li>
            <li><strong>Maintain Warranty:</strong> Many manufacturers require annual maintenance to keep your warranty valid.</li>
            <li><strong>Better Comfort:</strong> A tuned-up AC maintains more consistent temperatures and better humidity control.</li>
            <li><strong>Improved Air Quality:</strong> Clean coils and fresh filters mean cleaner air for your family.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>How Often Should You Get an AC Tune-Up?</h2>
