          <ul>
            <li><strong>Spring:</strong> Schedule a tune-up in March or April before the cooling season begins</li>
            <li><strong>Fall (Optional):</strong> A second tune-up in October can catch issues from the summer season</li>
          </ul>
          <p>At minimum, your AC should be professionally serviced once per year. Twice-yearly service is ideal for systems that run year-round.</p>

